
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About";
}

<div class="container mb-4 view-text">
    <h2 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 4vh; font-weight: bolder; margin-top: 3.5vh">@ViewData["Title"]</h2>
    <hr />

    <div class="text-light">
        Welcome to <span style="font-weight: bolder">FitnessHub - Global Network</span>, your ultimate destination for health, fitness, and well-being.<br />
        With locations in every country across the globe, FitnessHub offers you the convenience of staying fit no matter where you are.<br />
        Our mission is to inspire and support individuals from all walks of life to reach their fitness goals and lead healthier lifestyles.<br /><br />

        <h5>Our Mission</h5>
        At FitnessHub, we believe that fitness is not just a destination but a journey.<br />
        We are committed to providing state-of-the-art equipment, certified trainers, and a wide variety of fitness classes to help you on your personal journey to health and wellness.<br /><br />

        <h5>Global Access</h5>
        As a global gym chain, FitnessHub provides members with unparalleled access to any of our gyms, no matter where you are in the world.<br />
        Whether you're at home, traveling for work, or on vacation, your membership gives you full access to all FitnessHub locations. We’ve got you covered!<br />
        Our global network ensures that you never miss a workout, no matter where life takes you.<br /><br />

        <h5>Our Facilities</h5>
        Our gyms feature top-tier equipment, spacious workout areas, and dedicated spaces for strength training, cardio, group classes, and personal training.<br />
        We also offer locker rooms, showers, and relaxation areas to ensure that you have a comfortable and enjoyable experience no matter which location you visit.<br /><br />

        <h5>Classes and Programs</h5>
        FitnessHub offers a variety of group classes tailored to all fitness levels.<br />
        Whether you're just starting your fitness journey or you're an experienced athlete, there's something for everyone.<br /><br />

        <h5>Our Teams</h5>
        Our teams of certified personal trainers, nutrition experts, and support staff are passionate about helping you achieve your fitness goals.<br />
        Every member of our teams is dedicated to providing personalized training plans and guidance to ensure you get the most out of your workouts.<br /><br />

        <h5>Join Our Global Community</h5>
        At FitnessHub, you're more than just a member – you're part of a vibrant, global community.<br />
        Our supportive and motivating environment makes it easy to stay committed to your fitness journey while forming lasting friendships along the way.<br />
        Enjoy the freedom of working out anywhere in the world, knowing that FitnessHub is always there to support you.<br /><br />

        <span style="font-weight: bolder">We look forward to welcoming you to FitnessHub and supporting you on your journey to a healthier, stronger you – wherever you are in the world.</span>
    </div>

</div>